{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act20side", "eventName": "理想城：長夏狂歡季", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IC-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "“大水坑”", "storyInfo": "杜林人們投票決定拆除“大水坑”。斯第奇和設計代表敘光決定以比稿來確定誰負責設計下一個際崖城地標，它將與鐵路橋同時建設。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g1_durinstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$relax_intro", "key": "$relax_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽說了嗎？那個勁爆的消息！", "name": "搓手的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪個？", "name": "心癢的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克羅綺說代表們正在商量著搞出點新東西！", "name": "搓手的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上次那個讓全城燈光變成綠色的計畫我可不太喜歡。", "name": "心癢的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是那個！是關於滑梯的！", "name": "搓手的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說斯第奇和卡奇正在吵“大水坑”的改建方案呢！", "name": "搓手的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們兩個嗎？！已經吵到哪一步了？", "name": "心癢的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，好像是用水炮把人打進另一個水炮，再打進另一個......之類的？", "name": "搓手的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g2_fountainlake", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絕對不行！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我再換個方案，用水炮把人打上高處的跳板......", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你除了水炮就說不出別的了是嗎？", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你給我的啟發！那麼大建築設計師斯第奇又有什麼好點子呢？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我本來只是打算作為總建築設計師，稍微把控一下那些阿卡胡拉人的方案的......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你讓地上人來幫忙造鐵路橋，我沒意見。但我們現在討論的，是在鐵路橋之上的，與鐵路橋共生的，際崖城的地標！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不同意我碰穹頂，可以，我完全理解你對穹頂的感情，那我們就討論大滑梯之後的下一個地標是什麼。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們完全可以更簡潔優美地處理這個問題，它可以充滿象徵性！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也可以更刺激！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#5$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也可以更刺激地充滿象徵性！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，卡奇，我們在這裡爭不出什麼東西。要比設計搞競標？完全可以，我們給彼此留出創作時間，然後讓際崖城的市民做選擇。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以，就和當年一樣。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也贊同——", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克羅綺小姐？你這是喝酒了嗎？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事啦，就喝了一點點。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喝了三桶。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇，你的方案我聽說了，我很有興趣。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然卡奇也不太反對，那事情就好辦了！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#8$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要再找到黛柯綺，我們就能推著際崖城搞出點新東西啦！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#9$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g4_durinsquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$holiday_intro", "key": "$holiday_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的意思是，我該換一種方式對待它們......", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不覺得它們很可愛嗎？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些小傢伙們的確還遠不能被稱作是“人”，我並不是醫生，但就算如此，我也知道人的複雜度是現在的機器還難以企及的。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這並不妨礙我們更加友善地和它們相處。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛柯綺，你是這些小傢伙的“家長”。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......家長，是嗎。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些小傢伙願意依賴你，願意相信你，就像剛剛破殼的羽獸在媽媽的翅膀下成長。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#5"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很長時間，我看待它們的態度......沒有那麼“關心”。我只是在做一個工業代表該做的，和一代代的工業代表沒什麼不同。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "機器人的管理員們從那些喜歡泡在圖書館機械區裡的杜林人中選拔而出，我們得掌握製造這些小東西的方法。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實並不複雜，只要按照書上說的去做，把自己喜歡的零件裝在一起......發揮自己的想像力，它們總能動起來。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的老師曾經花費了很多年想要搞清楚這些小傢伙運轉的原理，不過最後毫無收獲。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說老師的老師也研究過，她成功讓助理機器人可以講笑話了。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#8$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道該怎麼激怒一個杜林人嗎？沒人知道！哈哈哈。", "name": "奇怪的機械0429"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，水準很高。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我，我只是理所當然地借助它們的力量。祖瑪瑪，你說得對，我應該試著和它們“交流”。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "0429，你的同伴0428已經退役，它無法透過檢修被喚醒。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它仍是我們的一員，它建設過的東西不會消亡。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "退役不是終點。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#8$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本機確認指令，退役不是終點。明白。", "name": "奇怪的機械0429"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祖瑪瑪定義了關係，朋友。黛柯綺，希望和你定義為朋友。", "name": "奇怪的機械0429"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朋友，是啊，朋友，我們還可以擁有這種關係。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#8$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "0429，你知道嗎？朋友之間就是會互幫互助的。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前我嫌麻煩的事情，我總是命令你們代我去做......", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想，這並不好。我們之間應該有更平等的相處模式。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#2$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之後，我會以朋友的身份拜託你們幫忙去做的。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#9$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到，幫助朋友。", "name": "奇怪的機械0429"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "0429，拜託你——", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#2$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "送三大箱麥酒去我家裡，再帶些零食。然後幫我跟耶奇大師說一聲，我在睡覺，今天的代表例會就不去了。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#9$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這不太對吧？", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#4"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祖瑪瑪！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，嘉維爾，你們來了！", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我的新朋友助理機器人0429和它的無良老闆黛柯綺。", "name": "森蚺"}, "figure_art": "char_416_zumama_1#1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黛柯綺，會議邀請，全體代表——", "name": "奇怪的機械0429"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "0429，任務變更，我依然以朋友的身份拜託你，幫個小忙，你去代我喊個到吧。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#9$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_416_zumama_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫助朋友，幫助朋友！", "name": "奇怪的機械0429"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_576_1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自己去！", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g7_durinhall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，我們上次這麼多人一起開會是為了什麼來著？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了酒類供應不足的問題。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有不足過嗎？", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#4$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個會你翹了。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#10$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，真是懷念啊，喜歡蜜釀的人為了不讓烈酒愛好者喝到酒，買空了際崖城的烈酒存貨。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了報復，烈酒愛好者協會的人也在城裡大肆收購蜜釀。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幫醉鬼喝不到酒活得下去？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "活不下去。於是他們開始喝本來只是為了報復仇家才囤的酒。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#5$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說那段時間，兩邊愛好者協會的會員對調了不少，哈哈！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜啊，他們還是不能理解漿果番茄酒的好。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#3$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#4$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡奇，你......你是喝漿果番茄酒的？", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，怎麼了？", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪不得各種酒類愛好者協會都沒有你......", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個......算了，關於讓我們聚在這裡的“大水坑”......", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同意拆除“大水坑”。越快越好。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#7$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也同意。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們不是還挺喜歡那裡的嘛！克羅綺，你每周都會去好幾次呢！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#3$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我後悔了，居然在喜歡漿果番茄酒的傢伙建的設施裡浪費了那麼多時間......恥辱。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#7$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "參與了這種人的項目......這是我作為工業代表的失職。", "name": "黛柯綺·銀幣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_569_1#6$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們兩個！喂，耶奇大師，你那是什麼表情。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#3$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，喜歡漿果番茄酒，確實有點......", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#10$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然諸位達成了共識，我們就號召大家把那個花裡胡哨的大滑梯炸掉，重新修通鐵路，解決耶奇大師擔心的問題，就這樣，沒意見吧？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然有點可惜，不過建築設計師不會讓過去的作品困住自己的。這是新的大展拳腳的機會。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇，你之前說你會和卡奇競標際崖城的新地標，這話是認真的吧。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？斯第奇，你終於又要出手了嗎？", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都說到這個份上了，我當然要拿出點真本事。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來接下來幾個月要精彩了啊，我得先囤點酒了。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，耶奇大師，要不要試試漿果番茄酒，真的沒那麼糟糕。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絕對不要。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#4$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g4_durinsquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dontmaketrouble_intro", "key": "$dontmaketrouble_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "計票——結束！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，按照大家的決議，“大水坑”的生命周期會就此完結。我們會重新修建鐵路橋，並將同時建設新的際崖城地標！", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好耶！正好也差不多玩膩了！", "name": "歡呼的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的方案來點不一樣的！聽說是雲霄飛車？", "name": "暢想的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "水上雲霄飛車！", "name": "歡呼的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旋轉水上雲霄飛車！", "name": "暢想的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彈射旋轉水上雲霄飛車！附帶超級水炮！再附帶自走車專用賽道！", "name": "歡呼的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "具體的設計方案，之後會由我和斯第奇分別提交，到時候會再次召集大家對方案進行表決。", "name": "卡奇·敘光"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_567_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個斯第奇？住在方盒子裡的斯第奇？", "name": "歡呼的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，幾年前我看過他的設計，雖然玩起來沒有那麼盡興，但也有一種獨特的美......", "name": "暢想的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許也可以開發玩法，畢竟那裡說白了就是場所，而重要的是在場所裡幹什麼！", "name": "歡呼的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總感覺斯第奇的建築會適合躺在那裡放空——", "name": "暢想的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《奇談怪論》裡介紹過的超放鬆高盧冥想！", "name": "歡呼的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_575_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，不是不行。", "name": "暢想的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_575_1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，事情似乎順利解決？雖然我們好像什麼都沒幹。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還是經歷了一些艱苦卓絕的談判的。對吧，克羅綺？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶奇老頭！快點喝！你在杯子裡養鱗呢？！", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_566_1#6$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳咳！我、我歇口氣！", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#7$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們幹了很多事呀，嘉維爾！我們一起買了一大堆東西，度過了一個不錯的假期，還幫阿卡胡拉攬下了個大項目呢。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還把我的心情搞得很糟。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼說嘛，我還以為我們的交情已經變好了。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，比想像的輕鬆點。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#8$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這說明你這小鬼本來也辦得到的，對吧。", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，接下來......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，你這副表情？", "name": "嘉維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_1026_gvial2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些日子沒動手了，有點......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，沒事，我只是需要重新熱身而已。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要我重新找回狀態，一定——", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}